Class LongRunningRecognizeMetadata.Builder 

public static final class LongRunningRecognizeMetadata.Builder extends GeneratedMessageV3.Builder<LongRunningRecognizeMetadata.Builder> implements LongRunningRecognizeMetadataOrBuilder
Describes the progress of a long-running `LongRunningRecognize` call. It is
 included in the `metadata` field of the `Operation` returned by the
 `GetOperation` call of the `google::longrunning::Operations` service.
